plot: Dolores contemplates her relationship with Paulie; Jennifer and Melissa discuss tensions; Margaret mourns husband's death; Danielle questions Teresa and Jennifer's loyalty at brunch, leading to arguments.

Dolores mulls over the next steps in her relationship with Paulie. Jennifer Aydin and Melissa sit down for a tense discussion about their ongoing issues. Margaret emotionally reflects on the strain in her marriage caused by Jan's sudden passing. At Danielle's Boujie Brunch, all hell breaks loose when Danielle questions Teresa and Jennifer's loyalty. Rachel and Teresa argue in defense of their husbands.
